data.description: Welcome to 3201 Brownsville Rd! Let the beautiful original woodwork invite friends and family to gather in this grand home!  Boast 5 full bedrooms, and 4 full levels of living space. Entertain guests on the back deck right off of the eat in kitchen. Or host dinner parties in the stately dining room with all original woodwork and built-ins. On a beautiful corner lot, there is PLENTY of parking both in the detached garage and the driveway. Close to everything Brentwood has to offer, yet only a quick trip to the city. Do not miss the chance to own a piece of history with this lovingly maintained home.
